data.description: Experience the ideal combination of comfort and convenience in this newly listed home in Jefferson City, TN. Situated in a picturesque, established neighborhood with private lake access, this property offers over 2500 SqFt of living space with modern upgrades and a spacious 2 car garage. Additionally, the home includes an extra lot totaling 3.89 acres, providing plenty of room and seclusion. Located just a short drive from popular dining and shopping spots, this gem is a must-see in East Tennessee near Cherokee Lake.Step inside to find a welcoming atmosphere, which features 3 bedrooms, 3 full bathroom including a spacious master suite with en suite bathroom and direct access to the deck. A partially fenced backyard, a partially finished basement, a cozy living room with a gas fireplace, and an additional living area with a walk-out onto the deck provide endless opportunities for relaxation and entertainment. Other features include a detached carport and gazebo.Don't miss the chance to call this exceptional property your own. Schedule your showing today!
